Package: SNVMutations
Type: Package
Title: What the package does (short line)
Version: 0.99.1
Date: 2023-02-26
Authors@R: 
    person("Michele", "Rossi", role = c("aut", "cre") , email= "Michele.rossi9@mail.polimi.it")
Description: Reads .vcf file, the reference genome and a desired length and returns a vector of SNVs in the format UP REF>ALT DOWN. The package also returns a count table of mutation. 
